{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-the-children-of-an-element-using-jquery","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"jquery","demoType":null,"title":"Selektuj potomke elementa koristeći jQuery","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada elementi HTML budu na istom nivou ispod drugog, nazivaju se <dfn>deca</dfn> tog elementa. Na primer, elementi dugmeta u ovom izazovu sa tekstovima <code>#target1</code>, <code>#target2</code>, i <code>#target3</code> su sva deca elementa <code>&#x3C;div class=\"well\" id=\"left-well\"></code>.</p>\n<p>jQuery ima funkciju nazvanu <code>children()</code> koja vam omogućava pristup potomcima bilo kog odabranog elementa.</p>\n<p>Evo primera kako da koristiš funkciju <code>children()</code> ili dodaš boju <code>left-well</code> za potomke tvog elementa <code>blue</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">$(\"#left-well\").children().css(\"color\", \"blue\")\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aed208826","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Postavi narandžastu boju za sve elemente tvog dela <code>right-well</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":6,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18320,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-the-children-of-an-element-using-jquery"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null},{"link":null,"src":"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<script>\r\n  $(document).ready(function() {\r\n    $(\"#target1\").css(\"color\", \"red\");\r\n    $(\"#target1\").prop(\"disabled\", true);\r\n    $(\"#target4\").remove();\r\n    $(\"#target2\").appendTo(\"#right-well\");\r\n    $(\"#target5\").clone().appendTo(\"#left-well\");\r\n    $(\"#target1\").parent().css(\"background-color\", \"red\");\r\n\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- Only change code above this line -->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h3 class=\"text-primary text-center\">jQuery Playground</h3>\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#left-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"left-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target1\">#target1</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target2\">#target2</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target3\">#target3</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#right-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"right-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target4\">#target4</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target5\">#target5</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target6\">#target6</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Svi deca za <code>#right-well</code> treba da imaju narandžastu boju.</p>","testString":"assert($('#right-well').children().css('color') === 'rgb(255, 165, 0)');"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da koristite funkciju <code>children()</code> za izmenu ovih elemenata.</p>","testString":"assert(code.match(/\\.children\\(\\)\\.css/g));"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da koristite jQuery samo za dodavanje ovih klasa elementu.</p>","testString":"assert(code.match(/<div class=\"well\" id=\"right-well\">/g));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#jquery","dashedName":"target-the-children-of-an-element-using-jque